    "**Outputs (under `OUT_DIR`):** deploy-winner FPs; TabPFN **per-threshold** counts + long CSV; legacy TabPFN threshold; union CSV; **`fp_mining_summary.json`** + **`kaggle_fp_outputs_manifest.json`** for reuse on Kaggle.\n"
